<% content_for :email_preheader, "Confirm your email address to finish setting up Miru." %>
<% content_for :email_eyebrow, "Account setup" %>
<% content_for :email_title, "Welcome to Miru" %>
<% content_for :email_subtitle do %>
  Confirm your email address to start tracking time, sending invoices, and managing your team from one place.
<% end %>

<p>Hi <strong><%= @resource.first_name.titleize %> <%= @resource.last_name.titleize %></strong>,</p>

<p>You're almost set. Here are a few of the things you can do with Miru from day one:</p>

<div class="email-panel email-panel-soft">
  <ul class="email-list">
    <li>Send professional invoices with hosted payment links.</li>
    <li>Track time, expenses, and utilization in one workflow.</li>
    <li>Manage your team, clients, and billing from a single workspace.</li>
    <li>Stay on top of revenue, overdue invoices, and payment activity.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p>Use the button below to confirm your email address.</p>

<%= render "shared/mailer/button", href: confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token), label: "Confirm email address" %>

<div class="email-divider"></div>

<p class="email-muted">If you did not create a Miru account, you can safely ignore this message.</p>

<p>Thanks,<br><strong>Team Miru</strong></p>
